<html
	xmlns:c = "http://www.classesarecode.net/pistol/core"
	xmlns:e = "http://www.classesarecode.net/pistol/entity"
	xmlns:i18n = "http://www.classesarecode.net/pistol/i18n"
	xmlns:md = "http://www.classesarecode.net/pistol/md"
	xmlns:string = "http://www.classesarecode.net/pistol/string"
	xmlns:html = "http://www.classesarecode.net/pistol/html">
	<head>
		<title>Pistol Documentation - string:ucwords</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1>string:ucwords</h1>
		<p>This tag will uppercase the first character of each word in a string, leaving all other characters intact.</p>
		<p><e:lt/>string:ucase<e:gt/>upper case words in THIS STRING<e:lt/>/string:ucase<e:gt/> will result in</p>
		<p><string:ucwords>upper case words in THIS STRING</string:ucwords></p>
	</body>	
</html>